item.description:
THIS EVENT IS CANCELLED SO SORRY FOR ANY INCONVENIENCE

Whether it's gossip, men, sex, family, friends - these ladies will cover it all and no topic is off limits. Grab your friends and get "pumped" up for this fabulous evening of non-stop energy and laughs!

Both men and women welcome!

Laugh and be entertained by Hilarious Female Comedians...

  • Lana Moore
  • Andrea Henry
  • Dana Cairns

Dinner Show doors open at 7 pm - the food is excellent!

Show Only doors open at 8 pm - please do not arrive prior to 8 pm if you are not having dinner.

Show starts at 8:30 pm

$45 dinner and show

$25 show only
Change the amount in the payment box when you RSVP for show only option.

When you arrive, follow signs to the show.  Check-in at the registration table and tell them you are with Jacki's Meetup Group.  Your name will be on the list and you will be escorted to our tables.

The host, Lane Moore, regularly performs stand-up, storytelling, and sketch comedy in NYC and Los Angeles. She has performed alongside some of the biggest names in comedy such as Aziz Ansari and Janeane Garofalo and Margaret Cho among others.
